    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Aporcelaimellus castaneanus sp. n. A: Anterior region in median view. B: Same in lateral, surface view. C: Female, posterior body region. D: Female, anterior genital branch. E: Pharyngeal expansion. F: Male, posterior body region. G: Male, entire body. H: Female, entire body. I: Spicule and lateral guiding piece. J: Vagina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214031/files/figure.png" ;
